metadata.name: Calmed Souls Edifice
metadata.description: Spirits that have become tired in the chaos and bustle of life have no choice to enter this edifice. An edifice filled with peace and kindness, nurturing the soul and teaching how one can find calmness and love oneself amidst the hustle and bustle of the world and technology. It teaches how to make peace with oneself and honor oneself. This building is in a hidden city, and those who truly need permanent peace from the bottom of their hearts take refuge there
